{"tid":1322460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田進退兩難 車公靈籤早警示","createTime":"2019-07-16T02:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T11:56:33.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0deb744a904d54c726b53ec1ac8aa52fa04dd0","tid":1322460,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E9%80%B2%E9%80%80%E5%85%A9%E9%9B%A3-%E8%BB%8A%E5%85%AC%E9%9D%88%E7%B1%A4%E6%97%A9%E8%AD%A6%E7%A4%BA-214500761.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E9%2580%25B2%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%259B%25A3-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%259D%2588%25E7%25B1%25A4%25E6%2597%25A9%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25A4%25BA-214500761.html&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=43d87c83\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E9%80%B2%E9%80%80%E5%85%A9%E9%9B%A3-%E8%BB%8A%E5%85%AC%E9%9D%88%E7%B1%A4%E6%97%A9%E8%AD%A6%E7%A4%BA-214500761.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/i7FTMIt4AMQFAJz1tMBA5A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/c693aaf7b202eb1623ad94e7e8887273\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fi7FTMIt4AMQFAJz1tMBA5A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fc693aaf7b202eb1623ad94e7e8887273&h=ad313e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車公靈籤八十二號下籤寓意沙田區進退兩難。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】周日（14日）的沙田反修例遊行，最終演變成示威者與警方的嚴重流血衝突。有網民於社交平台上載了沙田鄉事委員會首副主席李志麒，在今年農曆大年初二於沙田車公廟為沙田區求得八十二號下籤。該籤籤文是︰「心中日復自思量，時運未通怎主張；進退難為無定處，恐防患禍與災殃。」發貼者於貼文指︰「尾兩句幾靈下」，亦有網民留言稱︰「有時真係唔到你唔信邪」。<br />\n<br />\n做事合情理 毋須怕批評<br />\n<br />\n車公靈籤第八十二籤籤頭是「姜太公渭水艱難」，解曰：「出入謹慎．凡事小心」。發貼者引述當時的大會解籤師傅指出，新一年社會上或有不同聲音和意見，令「主持者」有壓力，但只要做事合情合理，便不會擔心批評者意見，並且心安理得。<br />\n<br />\n有網民就稱︰「原來支簽（籤）係講沙田居民同示威者」，亦有網民指，「進退難為無定處」就如前日示威者的處境。堪輿學家麥玲玲今年二月接受本報訪問時，亦提到今年沙田宜靜不宜動，「自己又未諗掂，時運又唔好，進退兩難」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家就係做事唔合情合理<br />\n仲點心安理得"},{"pid":"e7ec2888d6e279b6abb64c04cce03115ed5d638d","tid":1322460,"uid":139475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"進退難為無定處<br />\n恐防患禍與災殃<br />\n車公<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}